name: GalaxyHistory
0: ”Alexa, what happened on this day in Galaxy history?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: galaxy history
des: Galaxy History allows you to look up your favorite facts about the Los Angeles Galaxy, the most successful team in Major League Soccer history. You can ask Alexa about events on any day to the birthday of players to who holds the most goals in a season. Enjoy this skill for all LA Galaxy fans.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
